WEBVTT

00:05.120 --> 00:08.950
我叫迈克尔·斯科菲尔德  我是一名逃犯
My name is Michael Scofield, I am a fugitive.

00:12.090 --> 00:17.190
三周前  我被关在巴拿马的一所监狱里
Three weeks ago, I was incarcerated In a Panamanian prison.

00:17.220 --> 00:18.850
在那里...
While I was there...

00:18.890 --> 00:21.250
公司找到了我
I was approached by the Company...

00:22.820 --> 00:23.820
公司是一个腐败堕落的...
The company is a corrupt organization...

00:23.850 --> 00:28.350
渗透到行业和政府中各个层面的组织
Involved in all levels of industry and government.

00:28.390 --> 00:30.150
他们给了我两个选择
They gave me two options.

00:30.540 --> 00:35.840
帮助他们的人詹姆斯·惠斯勒越狱
Break one of their men. James Whistler out of that prison.

00:35.870 --> 00:39.240
否则就杀了我最爱的女人
Or they would kill the only woman I ever loved.

00:39.270 --> 00:42.470
莎拉·唐克雷蒂医生
Dr. Sara Tancredi.

00:43.120 --> 00:47.020
我遵守了承诺  帮助惠斯勒成功越狱
I held up my end of deal and I broke Whistler out.

00:47.050 --> 00:48.690
但公司...
But the Company...

00:50.650 --> 00:53.190
还是杀了莎拉
They killed Sara anyway.

00:56.090 --> 00:59.190
我不知为何公司要詹姆斯·惠斯勒越狱
I don't know why the Company wanted James Whistler out of prison.

00:59.240 --> 01:03.050
但我跟踪他来到了洛杉矶
But I've tracked him here to Los Angeles.

01:03.090 --> 01:07.350
他和一位叫格雷琴的公司的特工在一起
He's with an another company agent I know only as Gretchen.

01:08.620 --> 01:10.990
就是杀害莎拉的那位特工
The same agent who murdered Sara.

01:12.150 --> 01:15.150
这一切要在今天了结
This ends today.

01:16.350 --> 01:17.750
我来这里寻求公正
I came here seeking justice.

01:17.790 --> 01:21.290
当前司法系统无法提供的公正
The justice that I now know the system cannot provide.

01:24.250 --> 01:27.490
所以如果你在读这封信的话...
So if you're reading this letter...

01:27.520 --> 01:30.220
你就明白我为给莎拉报仇在所不惜
You'll know I died avenging Sara's death.

