02:08.360 --> 02:10.560
你不用担心
Don't you worry about that.

02:10.610 --> 02:13.860
只要你们尽快回来就行
You worry about getting your ass back in that seat in time.

02:16.360 --> 02:19.760
如果你做成这件事  可以到我的房间...
If you pull this off, you can come up to my room later...

02:19.790 --> 02:22.460
我是绝对不会拒绝的
and the word "no" won't be in my vocabulary.

02:22.510 --> 02:25.360
确保我们拿到钱就好
Just make sure we get paid.

02:59.220 --> 03:01.260
快去快回
In and out.

03:45.760 --> 03:47.160
很高兴再次见到你
Good to see you again.

03:47.190 --> 03:48.860
我也是
You, too.

03:48.890 --> 03:50.260
很久没有你的消息了
Didn't hear from you for a while.

03:50.290 --> 03:51.460
开始怀疑你是否还感兴趣了
Started to wonder if you were still interested.

03:51.490 --> 03:53.120
当然  很感兴趣
I am, very much so.

03:53.160 --> 03:55.620
我需要非常的小心
Well, I needed to approach this carefully.

03:55.660 --> 03:57.420
我相信你一定会理解的
I'm sure you understand.

03:58.560 --> 04:00.560
你为谁买的
Who you buying it for?

04:00.580 --> 04:02.260
竞争对手
A competitor?

04:02.290 --> 04:03.660
-其他国家  -杰森
-A foreign country? -Jason.

04:03.680 --> 04:06.260
你知道我不可能告诉你的
You know I can't get into that.

04:06.260 --> 04:07.960
我们已经谈了几个月了
Now, we've been negotiating this for months.

04:07.980 --> 04:09.620
我答应了你所有的要求
I've jumped through all your hoops.

04:10.260 --> 04:12.960
同意在这里和你见面
I've agreed to meet you here.

04:14.620 --> 04:17.890
你到底想不想把数据卡卖给我
Do you want to sell the card to me or not?

04:29.260 --> 04:31.260
很快回来
Be right back.

04:45.260 --> 04:48.790
这块小塑料卡里有很多秘密
That's a lot of secrets on a little piece of plastic.

04:48.820 --> 04:51.190
我给你一点建议
Let me give you a little bit of advice.

04:51.220 --> 04:55.320
免费的建议
And this is on the house.

04:55.360 --> 04:57.460
拿着那东西要小心点
Watch your step with that thing.

04:57.480 --> 04:59.960
公司为了夺回它会不惜一切代价
The Company will do anything to get it back.

04:59.980 --> 05:02.260
我难道不知道吗
Don't I know it.

05:30.860 --> 05:32.660
-什么事  -你到底在干什么
-Yeah? -What the hell are you doing?

05:32.680 --> 05:33.980
我们得马上离开这里
We got to get out of here.

05:34.020 --> 05:35.360
我要把枪藏好
I need to hide the gun.

05:35.380 --> 05:37.250
把枪带在身上
Take the gun with you!

05:47.950 --> 05:49.250
快呀
Come on.

05:49.780 --> 05:52.350
她在哪
Where is she?

05:53.310 --> 05:56.180
迈克尔  你不明白
Michael, you don't understand.

05:56.210 --> 05:59.210
给格雷琴打电话  让她马上来这儿
Call Gretchen, get her in here now.

05:59.250 --> 06:00.780
你得相信我
You have to trust me.

06:00.810 --> 06:02.350
我不是你的敌人  迈克尔
I'm not your enemy, Michael.

06:02.380 --> 06:03.750
詹姆斯
James.

06:06.180 --> 06:07.910
我们得快离开
We need to leave.

06:07.950 --> 06:10.280
知道吗  无论如何...
You know, despite everything...

06:10.310 --> 06:12.450
即使现在莎拉还活着 她也会让我别杀你
If Sara could weigh in right now. She'd tell me not to kill you.

06:12.480 --> 06:14.650
她就是这样的人
That's the kind of person she was.

06:15.010 --> 06:17.310
你就是把这样的人从我身边夺走了
That's the kind of person you took from me.

06:17.350 --> 06:19.650
詹姆斯  难道你没告诉他吗
James, didn't you tell him?

06:19.980 --> 06:21.250
-他刚刚才...  -闭嘴
-He walked in five... -Shut up!

06:21.280 --> 06:23.580
格雷琴  看着我
Gretchen, look at me.

06:25.180 --> 06:26.350
这个为了莎拉
This is for Sara.

06:26.380 --> 06:27.750
我没杀莎拉
I never killed Sara.

06:27.780 --> 06:30.650
我就知道你这样的人是不会坦然承认的
I wouldn't expect someone like you to take this with dignity.

06:30.680 --> 06:33.160
我发誓她还活着
I swear to God she's alive.

06:33.750 --> 06:35.450
别侮辱我  也别侮辱她
Don't insult me and don't insult her.

06:35.480 --> 06:36.910
她逃掉了
She escaped.

06:36.950 --> 06:39.350
我们清楚如果你知道  我们就没有任何筹码了
We knew if you found out we wouldn't have any leverage.

06:39.380 --> 06:41.450
我编造了整件事
I fabricated the whole thing.

06:41.480 --> 06:43.260
我哥哥看到了...
My brother saw... 

06:43.270 --> 06:45.480
箱子里的人头 是另一具尸体上的
From a cadaver.A head in a box!

06:45.510 --> 06:47.150
你问问林肯他看到的到底是什么
You ask Lincoln what he really saw.

06:47.180 --> 06:48.750
-听她说  迈克尔  -别对我撒谎
-Listen to her, Michael. -Don't lie to me.

06:48.780 --> 06:50.280
我没撒谎  林肯上当了
I'm not lying to you. Lincoln bought it...

06:50.310 --> 06:53.180
你也上当了  骗局成功了
You bought it, it worked.

06:54.250 --> 06:56.180
迈克尔
Michael.

06:56.210 --> 06:57.450
那她在哪
Then where is she?

06:57.480 --> 06:58.980
我们出去后  我就告诉你
I'll tell you when we get outside.

06:59.010 --> 07:02.080
现在  我们要先离开这里
Right now, we need to get out of here.

07:02.150 --> 07:03.280
他们发现尸体了
They found the bodies.

07:06.010 --> 07:07.750
-把枪给我  -她在撒谎
-Give me the gun. -She's lying.

07:07.780 --> 07:08.910
是吗
Is she?

07:08.950 --> 07:10.780
如果你扣动扳机  就永远不会知道答案了
If you pull that trigger, you'll never know.

07:10.810 --> 07:12.710
杀了他  詹姆斯
Kill him, James.

07:12.750 --> 07:13.780
闭嘴
Shut up.

07:13.810 --> 07:15.010
她在哪
Where is she?

07:15.050 --> 07:16.550
莎拉在哪
Where is Sara.

07:16.580 --> 07:18.080
迈克尔
Michael.

07:18.110 --> 07:20.210
如果你不把枪给我
If you don't give me that gun.

07:20.250 --> 07:22.210
我就打爆你的头
I'm going to shoot you in the head.

07:33.760 --> 07:35.830
我们走
Let's go.

07:39.130 --> 07:41.630
我们在罗斯福酒店发现两具尸体
We got a double homicide at the Roosevelt Hotel.

08:01.390 --> 08:03.490
莎拉
Sara

08:09.010 --> 08:10.730
莫哈维沙漠  加州
Mojave desert, california.

08:25.250 --> 08:29.390
你知道完美成功的行动和失败的行动...
Do you know the difference between a perfectly executed operation...

08:29.420 --> 08:31.190
之间的区别吗
And a failed mission?

08:31.220 --> 08:34.650
-长官  -取决于小团队的领导力
-Sir? -It's small unit leadership.

08:34.690 --> 08:36.490
盟军用了两年半时间...
The Allies spent two and a half years...

08:36.520 --> 08:38.550
策划进攻诺曼底
Planning the invasion of Normandy.

08:38.590 --> 08:40.490
但在登陆日那天  一排滩头上的...
But on D-Day it came down to a handful of men...

08:40.520 --> 08:42.820
一小股部队...
On a strip of beach...

08:42.850 --> 08:45.250
来决定整个世界的命运
To decide the fate of the world.

08:45.660 --> 08:47.760
格雷琴  我想说的是...
What I'm getting at, Gretchen...

08:47.790 --> 08:50.420
即便是最好的计划...
Is even the best plan is only as good...

08:50.460 --> 08:53.290
也需要有人去执行才会成功
As the moving parts on the ground executing it.

08:53.320 --> 08:55.560
-将军  我们拿到了数据卡  -有什么问题吗
-General, we got your card. -what's the problem?

08:57.160 --> 08:59.820
我们什么都没拿到  这是赝品
We have nothing. It's a duplicate.

08:59.860 --> 09:02.220
几乎一模一样  但是个赝品
Almost flawless, but a duplicate.

09:02.590 --> 09:04.560
这不可能  我看到...
That's impossible, I saw...

09:04.590 --> 09:06.360
你知道夺回数据卡对我来说...
You know how important the retrieval of this card...

09:06.390 --> 09:08.120
有多重要  格雷琴
Is to me, Gretchen.

09:08.160 --> 09:09.960
你知道这是一个很可能...
You know that this is a security breach...

09:09.990 --> 09:13.960
对公司产生灾难性的后果的安全隐患
that could have catastrophic ramifications for the Company.

09:14.220 --> 09:16.420
我想唯一的可能就是...
The only thing I can think of...

09:16.460 --> 09:19.720
当惠斯勒灭口的时候  有段时间可以做手脚
There was a blind spot when Whistler was hitting the target.

09:19.790 --> 09:22.590
他可能复制了一份  并且还保留着原件
Maybe he made a duplicate and he still has the original.

09:22.620 --> 09:24.390
你雇用了他
You hired him.

09:25.360 --> 09:26.930
你对他委以重任
You kept him at the tip of the spear.

09:26.960 --> 09:29.490
你坚持要把他从索纳监狱捞出来
You insisted that we get him out of Sona.

09:29.530 --> 09:30.960
我们别无选择
We had to.

09:30.990 --> 09:33.060
他当时已经和目标联系上
He had already made contact with the target.

09:33.090 --> 09:35.190
当时  他是唯一的选择  长官
At that point, it was him or no one, sir.

09:35.230 --> 09:38.790
你能从这件事中得到什么好处
What's your stake in all of this?

09:38.830 --> 09:41.730
这件事与我无关  是惠斯勒一手策划的
I had nothing to do with it, Whistler acted on his own.

09:41.760 --> 09:43.090
我向你发誓
I swear to you.

09:44.160 --> 09:46.790
将军  我会补救的
General, I can fix this.

09:46.830 --> 09:48.330
你训练了我
You trained me.

09:48.360 --> 09:49.860
显然训练的不够好
Not well enough, apparently.

09:54.230 --> 09:55.860
你知道该怎么做
You know what to do.

09:58.690 --> 09:59.760
求求你
Please.

09:59.790 --> 10:01.760
我在迪拜有一个帐户
I have a bank account in Dubai.

10:01.790 --> 10:04.530
存有眼镜蛇2次行动中的贿金  是你的了
Left over from a slush fund from COBRA II, it's yours.

10:04.730 --> 10:05.860
不  求求你  求求你
No, please, please.

10:07.860 --> 10:10.860
巴拿马城  巴拿马
Panama City, Panama.

10:13.930 --> 10:15.230
你好
Hello.

10:15.260 --> 10:17.490
是我
Hey, it's me.

10:17.530 --> 10:18.760
你在哪  兄弟
Where are you, man?

10:18.790 --> 10:19.930
洛杉矶
Los Angeles.

10:19.960 --> 10:20.930
你还好吗  迈克尔
You okay, Michael?

10:20.960 --> 10:23.530
是的  我很安全
No, I'm, I'm safe.

10:23.560 --> 10:25.360
谢天谢地
Thank God, thank God.

10:25.390 --> 10:27.130
LJ和索菲亚怎么样
How's LJ and Sofia?

10:27.530 --> 10:31.290
他们...我正看着他们呢
Yeah, they're...I'm staring at them right now in fact.

10:31.330 --> 10:32.990
他们很好
They're fine.

10:33.030 --> 10:34.230
听说索纳监狱的事了吗
You hear about Sona?

10:34.260 --> 10:35.190
怎么了
What about it?

10:35.230 --> 10:37.530
三天前被囚犯夷为平地了
Burned down three days back by the inmates.

10:37.580 --> 10:40.530
囚犯暴乱了  没有贝里克  蒂博格和苏克雷的迹象
They rioted. no sign of Bellick, T-Bag, or Sucre.

10:40.990 --> 10:42.260
苏克雷
Sucre?

10:42.290 --> 10:43.930
他被抓了  我不知道原因
He got popped, I don't know how.

10:43.980 --> 10:45.360
报纸上登出了囚犯名单...
I mean, the papers listed the names of the inmates...

10:45.390 --> 10:47.760
监狱烧毁之前他在里面
And he was in there when it went down.

10:48.730 --> 10:50.930
我找到惠斯勒和格雷琴了
I found Whistler and Gretchen...

10:55.190 --> 10:56.860
格雷琴说...
Gretchen said...

10:58.860 --> 11:01.030
她说莎拉还活着
She said Sara is still alive.

11:03.530 --> 11:05.790
你究竟看到了什么  林肯
What did you see, Linc?

11:05.830 --> 11:07.590
你是什么意思  迈克尔
What do you mean what did I see, Michael?

11:07.630 --> 11:09.860
我要你告诉我  你到底看到了什么
I need you to tell me exactly what you saw.

11:09.890 --> 11:11.190
迈克尔  莎拉已经死了
Michael, Sara's gone.

11:11.530 --> 11:14.160
你说是在一个车库里  对吗  所以那一定很暗
You said it was in a garage, right? So it was dark.

11:14.190 --> 11:16.290
对  是很暗
Yeah, it was dark.

11:18.330 --> 11:20.530
但是如果你是在问  我是否拿起头...
But if you're asking me if I picked up the head...

11:20.560 --> 11:24.090
检查是不是莎拉  不  迈克尔  我...
To check to see if it was Sara, no, Michael, I-I...

11:24.130 --> 11:27.490
LJ说他...
LJ said he...

11:27.530 --> 11:29.260
他只是听到他们杀了莎拉  对吗
He only heard them kill Sara, right?

11:29.290 --> 11:31.430
你快回来吧  拜托
You just got to come back, please.

11:31.460 --> 11:33.090
回来吧  我们一起...
Come back. Let's just...

11:33.130 --> 11:34.660
一起开始新生活
Let's just start a new life.

11:34.690 --> 11:37.090
替我向索菲亚问好
Tell Sofia I said hi.

11:37.130 --> 11:38.890
告诉LJ...
And tell LJ...

11:38.930 --> 11:40.890
告诉他  他叔叔很爱他
Tell him his uncle loves him.

11:40.930 --> 11:43.060
迈克尔  别这样  求你了
Michael, don't do this, please.

11:53.060 --> 11:55.830
亚利桑那沙漠  距离墨西哥边境5公里
Arizona Desert, 5 miles from the mexican border.

12:04.960 --> 12:06.430
出来  出来
Out, out!

12:06.460 --> 12:08.860
你该换一个好点的通风设备  朋友
You need some better ventilation back there, amigo.

12:10.190 --> 12:11.130
想要翻译一下吗
Want to translate that?

12:11.160 --> 12:12.090
不用了
Don't worry about it.

12:12.130 --> 12:13.260
谢谢
Gracias.

12:16.830 --> 12:17.830
你妈妈在哪儿
Where's your mom?

12:17.860 --> 12:18.760
她会来的
She'll be here.

12:18.790 --> 12:19.960
