What do you mean she'll be here?

12:19.990 --> 12:21.060
我们没时间了
We're running out of time.

12:21.090 --> 12:22.660
-我得赶过去  -别担心
-I got to be up there. -Don't worry.

12:22.690 --> 12:24.030
我妈妈不会让我失望的
My mom wouldn't let me down.

12:26.190 --> 12:27.930
至少  目前还没有
At least, she hasn't yet.

12:29.190 --> 12:31.230
布莱利  这里
Bradley, over here!

12:31.430 --> 12:32.860
妈妈  妈妈
Mom! Mom!

12:32.890 --> 12:35.190
我告诉过你的  别担心  你会准时到的
I told you! Don't worry, you'll make it there!

12:45.990 --> 12:47.190
网址是什么
What is it called?

12:47.230 --> 12:49.230
EuropeanGoldfinch.net
EuropeanGoldfinch.net

12:49.260 --> 12:51.730
我们可以用它联系
It's what we can all use to communicate.

13:06.260 --> 13:09.260
迈克尔·斯科菲尔德  我有莎拉的消息
MS: I have info on Sara.

13:20.530 --> 13:21.530
迈克尔
Michael

13:27.630 --> 13:30.260
别紧张  我是一个人
Don't worry, I'm alone.

13:30.460 --> 13:31.560
很高兴见到你
It's good to see you.

13:31.600 --> 13:33.200
